<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 26 日星期五 19:17:18 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Spanish Court to Probe 3 Football Fans Over Racist Insults Against Real Madrid's Vinicius]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110616902" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/0f/1105488317_0:0:2644:1763_1440x900_80_0_1_a6ac6ef639a85248a66d6d79c4fe6cf0.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1105488159" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/spanish-court-to-probe-3-football-fans-over-racist-insults-against-real-madrids-vinicius-1110616902.html?share-img=1105488159"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Andre Penner</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">巴西足球运动员 Vinicius Junior 在巴西和瑞士之间的世界杯 G 组足球比赛中进球后庆祝</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Бразильский футболист Винисиус Жуниор  празднует забитый гол во время футбольного матча группы G чемпионата мира между Бразилией и Швейцарией  - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="巴西足球运动员小维尼修斯在巴西和瑞士之间的世界杯 G 组足球比赛中进球后庆祝" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/0f/1105488317_0:0:2645:1487_1920x0_80_0_0_bd994621ecee21930f4778887f94a916.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/0f/1105488317_0:0:2645:1487_640x0_80_0_0_79aa417474e8d3563a5a28021ebdfd8e.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/0f/1105488317_0:0:2645:1487_1280x0_80_0_0_98f9d42c7acd7261d3618eed8016d42e.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0c/0f/1105488317_0:0:2645:1487_1920x0_80_0_0_bd994621ecee21930f4778887f94a916.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Andre Penner </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据马德里（人造卫星）网报道：周五，西班牙城市瓦伦西亚的一家法院对三名球迷展开调查，他们在上周日皇家马德里和瓦伦西亚的比赛中对皇家马德里球员小维尼修斯大喊种族主义侮辱。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <em>“瓦伦西亚第 10 调查法庭负责人已启动初步程序，调查针对皇家马德里球员 Vinicius Junior 的种族主义侮辱......法庭在收到一份可能的仇恨犯罪报告后开始了诉讼程序瓦伦西亚社区高级警察总部信息旅，”司法总委员会在一份声明中说。</em></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">作为受害者的维尼修斯将能够通过视频会议作证。法庭还将要求瓦伦西亚足球俱乐部公布比赛当天在球场工作的保安人员的姓名，以便在调查中传唤他们作为证人。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">周日，西甲联赛第35轮， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230211/real-madrid-secures-its-fifth-fifa-club-world-cup-victory-beating-al-hilal-53-1107347552.html" target="_blank">皇马</a>在客场0-1不敌瓦伦西亚。由于看台上针对维尼修斯的种族主义辱骂，比赛在下半场中途停止。赛后，皇马主帅<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20220413/real-madrid-boss-carlo-ancelotti-is-proud-of-his-teams-stunning-ucl-comeback-against-chelsea-1094722566.html" target="_blank">安切洛蒂</a>表示，瓦伦西亚球迷称他的球员为“mono”，在西班牙语中是“猴子”的意思。维尼修斯本人表示，西班牙正在成为一个种族主义国家。西班牙警方称，事件发生后，三人被捕。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">西班牙皇家足球联合会 (RFEF) 周三表示，他们已经对这起事件展开了自己的调查，并补充说，它已经在两个赛季中就对维尼修斯的侮辱向西班牙各当局提出了九起投诉。瓦伦西亚表示，将禁止肇事者终生观看其比赛。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">今年 1 月，四名年龄在 19 至 24 岁之间的男子，据称属于马德里竞技队的一群狂热分子，在球队前一天在皇家马德里训练中心附近的一座桥上挂了一件仿制的 Vinicius 白衬衫。踢过马德里竞技。马德里主审法院表示，5 月 25 日，他们被指控犯有仇恨罪和违反道德操守罪。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 19:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/spanish-court-to-probe-3-football-fans-over-racist-insults-against-real-madrids-vinicius-1110616902.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/spanish-court-to-probe-3-football-fans-over-racist-insults-against-real-madrids-vinicius-1110616902.html<category>超越政治</category><category>足球明星</category><category>足球</category><category>运动</category><category>皇家马德里队</category><category>皇家马德里</category><category>种族主义</category><category>卡罗·安切洛蒂</category><category>瓦伦西亚</category><category>马德里</category><category>西班牙</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Failure to Reach US Debt Ceiling Deal Would Cause Contraction in US, World Economies - IMF]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110616778" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/03/1106952310_0:0:3000:2000_1440x900_80_0_1_b6e4bdabfeb7f66a7c35102f2261ffee.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1106952292" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/failure-to-reach-us-debt-ceiling-deal-would-cause-contraction-in-us-world-economies---imf-1110616778.html?share-img=1106952292"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 美联社照片 / Itsuo</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Inouye 2012 年 10 月。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="A woman sits in front of an International Monetary Fund logo at the venue of the IMF and World Bank meeting, Wednesday, Oct. 10, 2012. - Sputnik International, 1920, 26.05.2023" title="10 月 10 日星期三，一名妇女坐在国际货币基金组织和世界银行会议会场的国际货币基金组织标志前。 2012 年 10 月。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/03/1106952310_0:0:3000:1688_1920x0_80_0_0_c6cd526e36f129da01f5f76e4f8f808e.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/03/1106952310_0:0:3000:1688_640x0_80_0_0_4c58bd015bcc5cf8420f3563300e78b8.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/03/1106952310_0:0:3000:1688_1280x0_80_0_0_0e3b1cb9381d3d82445c8a5fa6d6c6a1.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/02/03/1106952310_0:0:3000:1688_1920x0_80_0_0_c6cd526e36f129da01f5f76e4f8f808e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / Itsuo Inouye </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：国际货币基金组织（IMF）总裁克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃周五表示，拜登政府和国会领导人未能就国家债务上限达成协议将导致美国和全球经济收缩。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">格奥尔基耶娃对记者说：“不可避免地，我们将处于美国和世界经济收缩的时期，这将令人震惊，震惊又震惊。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">她还认为，美国国债仍然可持续，即使在 6 月初出现有史以来首次违约的风险下，美国经济也有很大的承受能力。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “对我们来说，底线是美国债务是可持续的。美国在进入应该让每个人都担心的领域之前还有很长的路要走，但可持续并不意味着它是最佳的，”格奥尔基耶娃坚称。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110616778" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/failure-to-reach-us-debt-ceiling-deal-would-cause-contraction-in-us-world-economies---imf-1110616778.html?share-block=1110616781" data-title="&quot;The bottom line for us is the US debt is sustainable. The US has a long way to go before it gets into the territory that should make everybody worry, but being sustainable doesn't mean that it is optimal,&quot; Georgieva insisted."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">美国目前陷入困境，因为共和党控制的众议院迄今拒绝延长该国的债务上限 - 已经达到的债务上限 - 因为共和党试图迫使民主党人同意大幅削减预算，否则后者会反对。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">除非美国立法者尽快就此事达成协议，否则美国最终可能会出现债务违约。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 19:01:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/failure-to-reach-us-debt-ceiling-deal-would-cause-contraction-in-us-world-economies---imf-1110616778.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/failure-to-reach-us-debt-ceiling-deal-would-cause-contraction-in-us-world-economies---imf-1110616778.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>美国债务</category><category>美国债务上限危机</category><category>国际货币基金组织</category><category>克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Russian Tor-M1 Weapon System Obliterates Airborne Threats in Ukraine]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="media__video"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/css/videoplayer/videoplayer.min.css?9fe0c0742"><div class="video-player " style="padding-top: 56.25%;" data-nosnippet=""><video id="video_1110614274" data-import-id="74497763" data-media-id="1110614274" data-articleid="1110612794" data-title="Watch: Russian Tor-M1 Weapon System Obliterates Airborne Threats in Ukraine" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/watch-russian-tor-m1-weapon-system-obliterates-airborne-threats-in-ukraine-1110612794.html" data-next-autoplay="false" data-length="51" playsinline="true" poster="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/1a/1110614310_0:1:1274:717_600x0_80_0_0_3206a724473c8285bfbf5141df50331c.jpg" preload="none" class="video-js vjs-fluid" width="100%" height="100%"><p class="vjs-no-js">要观看此视频，请启用 JavaScript，并考虑升级到支持 HTML5 视频的网络浏览器</p></video><div class="video_info" data-customer-type="main" data-media-id="1110614274" data-import-id="74497763" data-article-id="1110612794" id="video_info__1110614274" data-video-length="51" data-video-type="" data-video-file-size="7212334" data-ads=""></div></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©人造卫星</div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">安德烈·德加林</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_dergalin_andrei/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:a.dergalin@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">乌克兰持续不断的冲突除其他外导致了一种说法的消亡，这种说法声称俄罗斯拥有陈旧的武器，根本无法与北约国家使用的装备竞争。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Tor-M1 防空系统是俄罗斯生产和部署的武器之一，在乌克兰冲突中证明了它们的价值，帮助俄罗斯军队免受基辅政权发动的空袭。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在一个例子中，部署在 Krasny Liman 附近前线的 Tor-M1 部队发现乌克兰无人机向俄罗斯军队移动，并在无人机有机会造成任何伤害之前迅速出动。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯国防部发布的一段短片展示了这种高效的防空武器在行动中的作用，因为 Tor-M1 与一个愚蠢到足以威胁俄罗斯军队的空中目标交战。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Fri, 26 May 2023 18:30:48 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/watch-russian-tor-m1-weapon-system-obliterates-airborne-threats-in-ukraine-1110612794.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230526/watch-russian-tor-m1-weapon-system-obliterates-airborne-threats-in-ukraine-1110612794.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>Tor-M1地对空导弹防御系统</category><category>视频</category></item></channel></rss>